Danny J. Hart



Mr. Danny J. Hart, Jr., is Vice President-Business Development at PDL BioPharma, Inc.
Mr. Hart was previously employed as an Associate by Hogan Lovells US LLP.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Washington and a graduate degree from Vanderbilt Law School.



